Personal Substrate Guide:
	
	Key:

	T = Turface All Sport 
	G = Granite Grit (Manna Pro 50lb. bag)
	P = Pumice (1/16" from GPP) 
	B = Pine Bark (sifted 2mm-10mm 'Soil Conditioner' from Lowe's)


Cactus:		4 T : 3 G : 1 P : 1 B  *next repot change to 4t4g1p1b*
Haworthia:	1 T : 2 G : 3 P
Adromischus:	4 T : 4 G : 2 P : 1 B  *maybe 2t2g1p1b*

Euphorbia:	4 T : 4 G : 1 P : 1 B
asclepiads:	2 T : 1 G : 1 P : 1 B


Osmocote (Indoor & Outdoor):

For NPK as labelled:

1.5 tbsp / gal. == 750 pellets / gal. == 75 pellets / 3" square pot


Still on hunt for cheaper pumice and/or lava rock


